Overview

This is a Profile Display Web Application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The application allows users to explore profiles, view details, and 
interact with an admin dashboard for managing profiles. It includes features like profile searching, profile management (add/edit/delete), and an interactive UI with animations.

